      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a fantastic, reliable ride for me, and it's still in really solid shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s all set for a new owner to jump in and start their own adventures. It drives like a dream and looks great parked in the driveway. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
