    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2017 Shelby GT350 is a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving 5.2L Voodoo V8 with its signature flat-plane crankshaft. Power is delivered through a crisp Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential with a 3.73 axle ratio. The chassis is sharpened by the MagneRide adaptive damping system, providing exceptional lateral grip and composure. Braking performance is anchored by Brembo six-piston fixed front calipers paired with heavy-duty cross-drilled rotors. While showing signs of spirited road use, the mechanical vitals remain robust, and the exhaust note from the active valve system is unmistakable. A well-sorted example for the driver who prioritizes track-bred engineering and visceral feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
