      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and aesthetic appeal without the showroom price tag. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, showing only minor imperfections from standard road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and well-preserved, with all features, from the climate control to the infotainment system, functioning exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and has been meticulously maintained according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, ensuring a smooth and confident driving experience. It has been primarily garage-kept and recently underwent a full professional detail, making it a turnkey option for its next owner.",
